      <div class="msgContentFrame">Well if we are talking concepts as well, I'd say Oil would be a great environmental condition. <br /> <br />When a character is in/covered in oil, fire damage has a chance to light them on fire and the fire lasts longer.  On the flip side, the character is more resistant to freezing/cold, so depending on what you are facing or using, it could be a handy weapon or shield.  There are plenty of skills that could cause it, like earth magic, or a ranger arrow.</div>
