      <div class="msgContentFrame"><b>Race:</b> Sylvari <br /> <br /><b>Profession:</b> Elementalist <br /> <br /><b>Skill Name:</b> Branchipulate <br /> <br /><b>Skill Description:</b> The skill 'Branchipulate' is a very useful skill in forests. The Sylvari elementalist casts a green spell and pushes it right into the ground. The ground colors a little green. The green area expands and expands until it finds a couple of trees around the enemy. The spell makes the trees become alive. The trees will then attack the opponent by hitting the opponent with its branches. This is a very powerful skill so the elementalist must wait two minutes before he can use 'Branchipulate' again. <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Nov 18th 2010  3:45pm by MystDisc </span></i></div>
